    • splitAndResolveOperation

      public void splitAndResolveOperation(ServerName serverName, Set<RemoteProcedureDispatcher.RemoteProcedure> operations, RSProcedureDispatcher.RemoteProcedureResolver resolver)
      Fetches RemoteProcedureDispatcher.RemoteOperations from the given remoteProcedures and groups them by class of the returned operation. Then resolver is used to dispatch RSProcedureDispatcher.RegionOpenOperations and RSProcedureDispatcher.RegionCloseOperations.
      Parameters:
      serverName - RegionServer to which the remote operations are sent
      operations - Remote procedures which are dispatched to the given server
      resolver - Used to dispatch remote procedures to given server.
